7 D. If the fee imposed or levied by subsection A of this
8 section, or any part of such amount, is not paid before the fee
9 becomes delinquent, there shall be collected on the total delinquent
10 fee interest at the rate of one and one-quarter percent (1 1/4%) per
11 month from the date of the delinquency until paid.
12 E. If any fee due under subsection A of this section, or any
13 part thereof, is not paid within fifteen (15) days after the fee
14 becomes delinquent, a penalty of ten percent (10%) on the total
15 amount of fee due and delinquent shall be added and paid.
16 F. All penalties or interest imposed by this section shall be
17 recoverable by the Tax Commission as a part of the fee imposed and
18 all penalties and interest shall be apportioned the same as the fee
