20 Environmental Quality for the purpose of administering the
21 requirements of the Oklahoma Used Tire Recycling Act; provided, in
22 no event shall either of the amounts allocated annually pursuant to
23 this paragraph exceed the 3-year average of the total fiscal year
24 amounts allocated in fiscal years 2015, 2016 and 2017 and any amount
